---
import PageHero from '../PageHero.astro';
---

<section class="relative w-full">
  <PageHero title="Services" eyebrow="What we do" />

  <!-- Intro copy -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 md:py-24 text-center">
    <p class="prose-body text-neutral-700">
      Voyaflair collaborates with hotels, tourism boards, and travel brands to create
      thoughtfully curated visual storytelling that captures the atmosphere, identity,
      and feeling of a destination.
    </p>
    <p class="prose-body text-neutral-700 mt-6">
      Through a blend of photography, cinematic video, and editorial-style storytelling,
      each collaboration is designed to create content that feels both inspiring and
      intentional — with a focus on meaningful travel experiences, aesthetic detail,
      and emotional connection.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>